      <title>中国考虑政府购买未售出房屋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-15/china-considers-government-purchases-of-unsold-homes-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社获悉，北京正在考虑一项让地方政府购买数百万套未售出房屋的提议，这将是迄今为止为挽救陷入困境的房地产市场最雄心勃勃的尝试之一。中国编辑詹姆斯·梅格和首席北亚记者斯蒂芬·恩格尔讨论了《彭博社：中国秀》的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-15/china-considers-government-purchases-of-unsold-homes-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 04:27:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国考虑政府购买未售出房屋以缓解供应过剩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/china-mulls-government-purchases-of-unsold-homes-to-ease-glut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，中国正在考虑一项提议，要求全国地方政府购买数百万套未售出房屋，这将是迄今为止为挽救陷入困境的房地产市场最雄心勃勃的尝试之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-15/china-mulls-government-purchases-of-unsold-homes-to-ease-glut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 May 2024 02:40:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
